data.description: Welcome to Rose Court Place, your charming haven of comfort and style! This home, nestled in McDonough, invites you to experience the convenience of townhome living! Built in 2004, this townhome has three beds, 2.5 baths, and a generous 1552 sq ft of living space. A brand-new roof with architectural shingles was installed in July 2023 The timeless allure of the brick exterior not only adds character but tells a story of low-maintenance living. As you step inside, you'll discover an intelligently designed home to maximize the use of space. Whether you're a family, a couple starting a new chapter, or someone seeking a cozy retreat, your ideal living space awaits. Convenience is a given, with local amenities or attractions nearby, making Rose Court Place not just a home but a lifestyle upgrade. Ready to turn the key and make Rose Court Place your own? Contact me today.
